com.tsgrp.migration.event.target

Class NodeContentFileWriterListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.event.target.NodeContentFileWriterListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener, TargetEndImportNodeEventListener

    public class NodeContentFileWriterListener
extends AbstractListener
implements TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener, TargetEndImportNodeEventListener
    Based on a configured attribute name, save content from the given node into a file location specified in the given Node Attribute (default is "om_target_file_location").

    MigrationNode Attributes Read

    • om_source_id
    • om_target_file_location
